Discover the mystery of the Schola Romana

   Children aged 7 to 12 take up the challenge by going to see characters
   in the museum who give them their secrets…

   READ MORE

Organise a business event in the museum

   Permanent and temporary exhibitions, an auditorium, a room for
   receptions and a roof terrace with a panoramic view of the town and the
   Arena. All these venues are modular and can be customised for your
   event.

