News from the museum

Discover the mystery of the Schola romana

   25 Sep 2018

   Excerpt:

   A discovery booklet for children 7 to 12 years old to live a historical
   experience. With Professor Antonin, the last member of this secret
   school, children take up the challenge of finding and joining the
   mysterious Schola Romana, starting by meeting certain characters in the
   museum who give them valuable clues. Available (in French and in…
